	<text>
		<body>
				<p rend="align(right)"><date>Wednesday&#44; 13 Tebeth&#44; &#40;February&#41;&#44; 1865</date>.</p>
				<p>Greetings to <sic>myfriend</sic> and the friend of the Most High&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I sent you four sheets of manuscript but there has been no<lb/> answer. Today&#44; I am sending you 22 sheets. I beg you for a quick re&#45;<lb/>turn of them. My conjecture about the Samaritans is found in the <hi rend="underline">Ba&#39;al</hi><lb/> <hi rend="underline">&#39;Akeda</hi>&#44; but without proof.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I am very much surprised not to find my article about the<lb/> seminary nor the one about the Spaniards in the &#8220;Occident&#8221;. I was<lb/> right that <persName>Illoway</persName><add>&#63;</add>&#44; as some one told me today&#44; has a great deal of<lb/> conflict in <placeName>New Orleans</placeName>. His reports were pure inventions. <persName>Szold</persName> is<lb/> the same kind of sloppy fellow&#44; whom the false mi...... [sic] permitted to<lb/> come there for his barmitzvah.... This <persName>Szold</persName> knows neither Hebrew<lb/> nor German....... Shall I report to <placeName>Pittsburgh</placeName> &#63; I shall.... and<lb/> ask why I did not go to <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>. If you have acquaintances there&#44;<lb/> write to me about it... Unfortunately&#44; my wife is sick. I am very confused &#40;upset&#41; my<lb/> <hi rend="underline"><persName>Esther</persName></hi> takes up much of my time.</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">With respect&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">Your very devoted&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(10)"><persName role="author">Jonah Bondi</persName></p>
				<p>In the <hi rend="underline"><placeName>Jeshurun</placeName></hi> I am in the company of <persName>Luzzato</persName>&#44; better than<lb/> <persName>Szold</persName>&#44; <persName>Wise</persName> and <persName>Illoway</persName>.</p>
				<p rend="&#40;The original letter is in very bad shape&#41;"></p>
			<pb n="Card"/>
				<p><persName>Mr. H. Nathan</persName>.</p>
				<p><placeName>29&#45;South 2nd St</placeName></p>
		</body>
